-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: -1.2em 8px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n        <p style=\"margin: -1.2em 8px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:inherit;\">新智元报道&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section></h3>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\">编辑：编辑部 HYZ</span>\n  </section>\n  <section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n     <h5 style=\"padding:10px;margin:10px 8px 0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;max-width:100%;word-break:break-all !important;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">【新智元导读】</strong>潞晨科技正式推出 Open-Sora 2.0——一款全新开源的SOTA视频生成模型，仅20万美元（224张GPU）成功训练商业级11B参数视频生成大模型。开发高性能的视频生成模型通常耗资高昂：Meta的视频模型训练需要6000多张GPU卡片，投入数百万美元。在多项关键指标上，它与动辄百万美元训练成本的模型分庭抗礼，全面提升视频生成的可及性与可拓展性。<strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"></strong></span></h5>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">今天，视频生成领域迎来开源革命！</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Open-Sora 2.0——全新开源的<strong>SOTA</strong>（State-of-the-Art）视频生成模型正式发布，仅用<strong>20万美元（224张GPU）</strong>成功训练出商业级11B参数视频生成大模型，性能直追HunyuanVideo和30B参数的Step-Video。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">权威评测VBench及用户偏好测试均证实其卓越表现，在多项关键指标上媲美动辄数百万美元训练成本的闭源模型。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">此次发布全面开源<strong>模型权重、推理代码及分布式训练全流程</strong>，让高质量视频生成真正触手可及，进一步提升视频生成的可及性与可拓展性。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n   <section style=\"color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, arial, sans-serif;\" data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"border-top:none;padding:10px;border-right:none;color:rgb(153, 153, 153);font-size:16px;line-height:1.75em;border-bottom:none;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;box-shadow:rgb(153, 153, 153) 1px 1px 2px;border-left:10px solid rgb(233, 233, 233);margin-top:5px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align: justify;\">GitHub开源仓库：</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align: justify;\">https://github.com/hpcaitech/Open-Sora</span><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align: justify;\"></span></strong></span></p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"504\" data-backw=\"578\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"505091266\" data-ratio=\"0.8722222222222222\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4ffe7566-278e-41d6-7d1d-759956572100/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4ffe7566-278e-41d6-7d1d-759956572100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\">体验与指标双在线</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <h3 style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">震撼视觉：Open-Sora 2.0 Demo先行</span></strong></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">观看宣传片，体验Open-Sora 2.0的强大生成能力：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_3895511555432955908\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1BlXTU9nvMibu4SSHslcg9icn64OzY9rw5IgbGyqQlDELibYuvGUelAoOLicL5YibOJUqRsjB6ChCxCBw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" data-ratio=\"1.7777777777777777\" data-w=\"1280\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3895511555432955908\"></iframe></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">动作幅度可控：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">可根据需求设定运动幅度，以更好地展现人物或场景的细腻动作。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"325\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"505091276\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/23035789-cebf-457b-7432-46fd0e9f3f00/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/23035789-cebf-457b-7432-46fd0e9f3f00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"325\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"505091277\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/06dd71f1-beb7-44f4-9bfa-13f917247400/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/06dd71f1-beb7-44f4-9bfa-13f917247400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">画质与流畅度：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">提供720p高分辨率和24 FPS流畅视频，让最终视频拥有稳定帧率与细节表现。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"325\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"505091278\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c59f4217-dfae-485b-407d-969a61578000/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c59f4217-dfae-485b-407d-969a61578000/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"325\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"505091280\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/42bcd757-fb5c-4c14-0e51-f63a6e940100/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/42bcd757-fb5c-4c14-0e51-f63a6e940100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">支持丰富的场景：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从乡村景色到自然风光场景，Open-Sora 2.0生成的画面细节与相机运镜都有出色的表现。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"325\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"505091279\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/374015e5-0fbf-4962-71e6-5165ada32200/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/374015e5-0fbf-4962-71e6-5165ada32200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"325\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"505091281\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/aede9304-8b2d-46aa-4db7-1cdae5532800/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/aede9304-8b2d-46aa-4db7-1cdae5532800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">11B参数规模媲美主流闭源大模型</span></strong></span></h3>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">·&nbsp;媲美HunyuanVide和30B Step-Video</span></strong>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Open-Sora 2.0采用<strong>11B参数规模</strong>，训练后在<strong>VBench</strong>和<strong>人工偏好</strong>（Human Preference）评测上都取得与用高昂成本开发的主流闭源大模型同等水平。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">·&nbsp;用户偏好评测</span></strong>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在视觉表现、文本一致性和动作表现三个评估维度上，Open Sora在至少两个指标上超越了开源SOTA HunyuanVideo，以及商业模型Runway Gen-3 Alpha等。以小成本获取了好性能。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"383\" data-backw=\"578\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"505091267\" data-ratio=\"0.57109375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/57ecd511-7e09-44dc-7c5a-ea6ca0beaf00/public\" style=\"width: 100%; pointer-events: initial;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/57ecd511-7e09-44dc-7c5a-ea6ca0beaf00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">·&nbsp;VBench 指标表现强势</span></strong>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">根据视频生成权威榜单VBench的评测结果，Open-Sora模型的性能进步显著。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从Open-Sora 1.2升级到2.0版本后，与行业领先的OpenAI Sora闭源模型之间的性能差距大幅缩小，从之前的<strong>4.52%</strong><strong>缩减至仅</strong><strong>0.69%</strong>，几乎实现了性能的全面追平。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">此外，Open-Sora 2.0在VBench评测中取得的分数已超过腾讯的HunyuanVideo，以更低的成本实现了更高的性能，为开源视频生成技术树立了全新标杆！</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"586\" data-imgfileid=\"505091224\" data-ratio=\"0.5305555555555556\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6b971f22-5b0b-44f2-1026-b441baa19c00/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1105\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6b971f22-5b0b-44f2-1026-b441baa19c00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\">实现突破：低成本训练与高效能优化</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Open Sora自开源以来，凭借其在视频生成领域的高效与优质表现，吸引了众多开发者的关注与参与。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而，随着项目的深入推进，也面临着高质量视频生成成本居高不下的问题。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为解决这些挑战，Open Sora团队展开了一系列卓有成效的技术探索，显著降低了模型训练成本。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">根据估算，市面上10B以上的开源视频模型，动辄需要上百万美元的单次训练成本，而Open Sora 2.0将该成本降低了5-10倍。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"234\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"505091291\" data-ratio=\"0.4046296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/357a7b06-8aeb-4230-1124-b808e9e93000/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/357a7b06-8aeb-4230-1124-b808e9e93000/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">作为开源视频生成领域的领导者，Open-Sora不仅继续开源了模型代码和权重，更开源了<strong>全流程训练代码</strong>，成功打造了强大的开源生态圈。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">据第三方技术平台统计，Open-Sora的学术论文引用量半年内获得近百引用，在全球开源影响力排名中稳居首位，领先所有开源的I2V/T2V视频生成项目，成为全球影响力最大的开源视频生成项目之一。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"304\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"693\" data-imgfileid=\"505091223\" data-ratio=\"0.5416666666666666\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3f258ddc-19ba-4de7-f46f-42cb1c80fa00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1280\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3f258ddc-19ba-4de7-f46f-42cb1c80fa00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <h3 style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">模型架构</span></strong></span></h3>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Open-Sora 2.0延续Open-Sora 1.2的设计思路，继续采用<strong>3D自编码器</strong>和<strong>Flow Matching训练框架</strong>，并通过<strong>多桶训练机制</strong>，实现对不同视频长度和分辨率的同时训练。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在模型架构上，引入<strong>3D全注意力机制</strong>，进一步提升视频生成质量。同时，采用最新的<strong>MMDiT架构</strong>，更精准地捕捉<strong>文本信息与视频内容的关系</strong>，并将模型规模从<strong>1B扩展至</strong><strong>11B</strong>。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">此外，借助<strong>开源图生视频模型FLUX</strong>进行初始化，大幅降低训练成本，实现更高效的视频生成优化。</span>\n  </section>\n  <h3 style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">高效训练方法和并行方案全开源</span></strong></span></h3>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了追求极致的成本优化，Open-Sora 2.0从四个方面着手削减训练开销。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">首先，通过<strong>严格的数据筛选</strong>，确保高质量数据输入，从源头提升模型训练效率。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">采用<strong>多阶段</strong><strong>、</strong><strong>多层次的筛选机制</strong>，结合多种过滤器，有效提升视频质量，为模型提供更精准、可靠的训练数据。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"270\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"686\" data-imgfileid=\"505091229\" data-ratio=\"0.48148148148148145\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4127d1a7-a0b4-406f-c7c4-281e568e0500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1426\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4127d1a7-a0b4-406f-c7c4-281e568e0500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">其次，高分辨率训练的成本远超低分辨率，达到相同数据量时，计算开销可能高达<strong>40倍</strong>。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">以<strong>256px、5秒</strong>的视频为例，其<strong>tokens数量约8千</strong>，而<strong>768px</strong>的视频<strong>tokens数量接近8万</strong>，相差<strong>10倍</strong>，再加上<strong>注意力机制的平方级计算复杂度</strong>，高分辨率训练的代价极其昂贵。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">因此，Open-Sora优先将<strong>算力投入到低分辨率训练</strong><strong>，</strong><strong>以高效学习运动信息</strong>，在降低成本的同时确保模型能够捕捉关键的动态特征。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"156\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"328\" data-imgfileid=\"505091228\" data-ratio=\"0.2777777777777778\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/62c2a5d9-2cc6-461e-1761-9832a44bc700/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1182\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/62c2a5d9-2cc6-461e-1761-9832a44bc700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">与此同时，Open-Sora<strong>优先训练图生视频任务</strong>，以加速模型收敛。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">相比直接训练高分辨率视频，图生视频模型在<strong>提升分辨率时具备更快的收敛速</strong><strong>度</strong>，从而进一步降低训练成本。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在推理阶段，除了<strong>直接进行</strong><strong>文本生视频（T2V）</strong>，还可以结合<strong>开源图像模型</strong>，通过<strong>文本生图再生视频（T2I2V）</strong>，以获得更精细的视觉效果。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">最后，Open-Sora采用<strong>高效的并行训练方案</strong>，结合<strong>ColossalAI</strong>和系统级优化，大幅提升计算资源利用率，实现更高效的视频生成训练。为了最大化训练效率，我们引入了一系列关键技术，包括：</span>\n  </section>\n  <ol class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\">高效的序列并行和ZeroDP</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\">，优化大规模模型的分布式计算效率。</span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\">细粒度控制的Gradient Checkpointing</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\">，在降低显存占用的同时保持计算效率。</span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\">训练自动恢复机制</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\">，确保<strong>99%以上的有效训练时间</strong>，减少计算资源浪费。</span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\">高效数据加载与内存管理</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\">，优化I/O，防止训练阻塞，加速训练流程。</span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\">高效异步模型保存</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\">，减少模型存储对训练流程的干扰，提高GPU利用率。</span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\">算子优化</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\">，针对关键计算模块进行深度优化，加速训练过程。</span></p></li>\n  </ol>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这些优化措施协同作用，使Open-Sora 2.0在<strong>高性能与低成本</strong>之间取得最佳平衡，大大降低了高质量视频生成模型的训练。</span>\n  </section>\n  <h3 style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">高压缩比AE带来更高速度</span></strong></span></h3>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在训练完成后，Open-Sora面向未来，进一步探索<strong>高压缩比视频自编码器</strong>的应用，以大幅降低推理成本。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">目前，大多数视频模型仍采用<strong>4×8×8</strong>的自编码器，导致<strong>单卡生成768px、5秒视频耗时近30分钟</strong>。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为解决这一瓶颈，Open-Sora训练了一款<strong>高压缩比（4×32×32）的视频自编码器</strong>，将推理时间缩短至单卡3分钟以内，推理速度提升<strong>10倍</strong>。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"178\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"484\" data-imgfileid=\"505091230\" data-ratio=\"0.3175925925925926\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c7fb5a48-8422-42fd-fbfc-c32739e6f200/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1524\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c7fb5a48-8422-42fd-fbfc-c32739e6f200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">要实现高压缩比编码器，需要解决两个核心挑战：<strong>如何训练高压缩但仍具备优秀重建效果的自编码器</strong>，以及<strong>如何利用该编码器训练视频生成模型</strong>。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">针对前者，Open-Sora团队在<strong>视频升降采样模块中引入残差连接</strong>，成功训练出一款<strong>重建质量媲美当前开源SoTA视频压缩模型</strong>，且具备<strong>更高压缩比</strong>的VAE，自此奠定了高效推理的基础。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"108\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"296\" data-imgfileid=\"505091231\" data-ratio=\"0.1925925925925926\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bad93d16-ef75-453c-0e63-ae537884af00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1538\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bad93d16-ef75-453c-0e63-ae537884af00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">高压缩自编码器在训练视频生成模型时面临<strong>更高的数据需求和收敛难度</strong>，通常需要<strong>更多训练数据</strong>才能达到理想效果。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为解决这一问题，Open-Sora 提出了<strong>基于蒸馏的优化策略</strong>，以提升<strong>AE（自编码器）特征空间的表达能力</strong>，并利用<strong>已经训练好的高质量模型</strong>作为初始化，减少训练所需的数据量和时间。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">此外，Open-Sora还<strong>重点训练图生视频任务</strong>，利用<strong>图像特征引导视频生成</strong>，进一步提升高压缩自编码器的收敛速度，使其在更短时间内达到一定生成效果。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Open-Sora认为，高压缩比视频自编码器将成为<strong>未来降低视频生成成本的关键方向</strong>。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">目前的初步实验结果已展现出<strong>显著的推理加速效果</strong>，希望能进一步激发社区对这一技术的关注与探索，共同推动高效、低成本的视频生成发展。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\">加入Open-Sora 2.0，共同推动AI视频革命</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">今天，Open-Sora 2.0正式开源！</span></strong>\n  </section>\n  <section data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n   <section style=\"\" data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <p style=\"border-top:none;padding:10px;border-right:none;color:rgb(153, 153, 153);font-size:16px;line-height:1.75em;border-bottom:none;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;box-shadow:rgb(153, 153, 153) 1px 1px 2px;border-left:10px solid rgb(233, 233, 233);margin-top:5px;text-align:left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;\">GitHub开源仓库：</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;\">https://github.com/hpcaitech/Open-Sora<br><strong>技术报告：</strong>https://github.com/hpcaitech/Open-Sora-Demo/blob/main/paper/Open_Sora_2_tech_report.pdf</span><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;\"></span></strong></span></p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">欢迎加入Open-Sora社区，探索AI视频的未来！</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Open-Sora 2.0，<strong>未来已来</strong>。让我们用更少的资源、更开放的生态，<strong>创造属于下一代的数字影像世界！</strong></span></section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "Open-Sora 2.0 开源视频生成模型，以低成本（20 万美元，224 张 GPU）实现商业级 11B 参数规模，性能媲美百万美元级闭源模型，并开源全流程训练代码。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Open-Sora 2.0 开源视频生成模型，以低成本（20 万美元，224 张 GPU）实现商业级 11B 参数规模，性能媲美百万美元级闭源模型，并开源全流程训练代码。",
  "summary": "Open-Sora 2.0 是潞晨科技推出的全新开源 SOTA 视频生成模型，相较于 1.2 版本，2.0 版本在模型架构上引入了 3D 全注意力机制和最新的 MMDiT 架构，并将模型规模扩展至 11B。它以极低的成本（20 万美元，224 张 GPU）训练出商业级 11B 参数的视频生成大模型，在 VBench 和用户偏好测试中表现出色，性能直追 HunyuanVideo 和 30B 参数的 Step-Video 等闭源模型。Open-Sora 2.0 全面开源模型权重、推理代码及分布式训练全流程，降低了高质量视频生成的门槛。该模型延续了 Open-Sora 1.2 的设计思路，采用 3D 自编码器和 Flow Matching 训练框架，并通过多桶训练机制提升视频生成质量。此外，Open-Sora 2.0 还通过严格的数据筛选、优先进行低分辨率训练、优先训练图生视频任务以及采用高效的并行训练方案等多种方式来削减训练开销，并探索高压缩比视频自编码器的应用以降低推理成本。",
